Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quadro 101, danos pesados.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quadro 193, quadro 318, contato perdido!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}No...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Retraia-se, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele pode disparar novamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Pai...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.49,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso atacar de verdade?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,É uma boa oportunidade.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Faça isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seja cuidadoso!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Reação de partículas Heigus poderosa \Nda segunda Gauna!
