Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.29,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se esta era o fim do mundo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:38.79,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e se minha vida estiver em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:38.79,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e se eu estiver prestes a morrer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:44.38,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:44.38,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}O que devo crer para viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.05,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.05,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se não fosse por ti, eu nunca sentiria dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.47,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então eu nunca teria sentido esta dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.47,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}arrancando meu coração de maneira cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:23:00.06,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}quebrando meu coração ao meio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:23:00.06,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer a dor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.81,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}é uma requisição rústica
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.81,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.27,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando até lá
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.27,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}não foi há muito tempo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:08.11,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:08.11,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um requiem ininterrupto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.03,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e mesmo agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.03,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ainda assim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:11.74,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}neste mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:11.74,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}探しています
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}desde agora em diante
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:17.12,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}para você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:17.12,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que diz respeito a você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.79,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.79,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também da alegria de nos encontrarmos
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.50,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o calor da sua presença
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.50,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o passar do seu tempo aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:28.72,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e a passagem do seu tempo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:28.72,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu tudo que você me fez eu lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.80,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.80,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:35.56,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Gelo cresce no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:35.56,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo o mapa do mar que eu chorei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.27,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sobre as feridas dentro de mim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.27,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também as cicatrizes que ficam no peito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:43.65,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu levo tudo comigo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:43.65,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}vou caminhar com todas as minhas forças
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:50.65,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e seguir meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:50.65,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu vou percorrer esta estrada
